### Create a deposit transaction
POST http://localhost:8080/api/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "ACC-00000",
  "toAccount": "ACC-12345",
  "amount": 1000.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "DEPOSIT"
}

###

### Create a transfer transaction
POST http://localhost:8080/api/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "ACC-12345",
  "toAccount": "ACC-67890",
  "amount": 100.50,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "TRANSFER"
}

###

### Create a withdrawal transaction
POST http://localhost:8080/api/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "ACC-67890",
  "toAccount": "ACC-00000",
  "amount": 50.25,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "WITHDRAWAL"
}

###

### Get all transactions
GET http://localhost:8080/api/transactions

###

### Get a specific transaction (replace {id} with actual transaction ID)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/transactions/{id}

###

### Get account balance for ACC-12345
GET http://localhost:8080/api/accounts/ACC-12345/balance

###

### Get account balance for ACC-67890
GET http://localhost:8080/api/accounts/ACC-67890/balance

